{"article_id":"59eqyaD8AJ4BHXYC","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Department of Homeland Security is set to conduct a series of massive deportation raids across the country","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"starting in January .","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"They ' ll mostly be targeting families","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"reportedly fleeing the rising violence in Central America","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"that have crossed the border within the past year","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"and have been ordered to leave by an immigration judge ,","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"according to the Washington Post :","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"The nationwide campaign ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"to be carried out by U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"( ICE )","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"agents as soon as early January ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"would be the first large-scale effort","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"to deport families","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"who have fled violence in Central America ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"those familiar with the plan said .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"More than 100,000 families with both adults and children have made the journey across the southwest border since last year ,","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"though this migration has largely been overshadowed by a related surge of unaccompanied minors .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"The ICE operation would target only adults and children","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"who have already been ordered removed from the United States by an immigration judge ,","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"according to officials familiar with the undertaking ,","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"who spoke on the condition of anonymity","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"because planning is ongoing","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"and the operation has not been given final approval by DHS .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"The adults and children would be detained","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"wherever they can be found","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"and immediately deported .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"The number","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"targeted","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"is expected to be in the hundreds and possibly greater .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"The proposed deportations have been controversial inside the Obama administration ,","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"which has been discussing them for several months .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"DHS Secretary Jeh Johnson has been pushing for the moves ,","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"according to those with knowledge of the debate ,","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"in part because of a new spike in the number of illegal immigrants in recent months . [ ... ]","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"Marsha Catron , a DHS spokeswoman , would not comment on any possible ICE operations","depth":4},{"id":35,"text":"but pointed out","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"that Johnson \" has consistently said","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"our border is not open to illegal immigration ,","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"and","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"if individuals come here illegally ,","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"do not qualify for asylum or other relief ,","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"and have final orders of removal ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"they will be sent back consistent with our laws and our values. \" [ ... ]","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Johnson has also made clear","depth":3},{"id":44,"text":"that families , children and others","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"who had illegally crossed the border recently","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"and did not obtain asylum status","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"- and anyone ordered deported","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"starting on Jan. 1 , 2014 -","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"would be subject to removal .","depth":4},{"id":50,"text":"The publication added","depth":4},{"id":51,"text":"that there would possibly be a backlash from Latino and immigration groups over this measure .","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"Gregory Chen , director of advocacy for the American Immigration Lawyers Association , said ,","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"\" \" It would be an outrage","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"if the administration subjected Central American families to even more aggressive enforcement tactics . \"","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Mark Krikorian , executive director of the Center for Immigration Studies , was mores skeptical in his words with the Post .","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"\" I ' ll believe it","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"when I see it , \"","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"\" What share is this going to be ? . . .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"It ' s a drop in the bucket","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"compared to the number","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"they ' ve admitted into the country .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"If you have photogenic raids on a few dozen illegal families","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"and that ' s the end of it ,","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"it ' s just for show .","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"It ' s just a [ public relations ]","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"thing , enforcement theater . \"","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"Of course , the 2016 Democratic field is n't pleased with these reported massive deportation plans ,","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"and this will surely continuing fueling the Trump machine","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"as we enter the new year .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Wow ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"because of the pressure","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"put on by me ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"ICE TO LAUNCH LARGE SCALE DEPORTATION RAIDS .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"It 's about time !","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"December 24 , 2015 .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"@ DHSgov holiday plans for raids","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"to round up/deport Central American refugees","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"fleeing death","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"are wrong .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"We are a better nation than this .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"- Martin O'Malley","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"( @ MartinOMalley )","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"December 24 , 2015","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"Christine and Katie wrote about the deluge of unaccompanied minors","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"that poured across the border last summer .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"At the time , Obama warned parents not to send their children alone to cross our borders illegally ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"noting","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"that they will be sent back","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"if they 're caught ,","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"along with the numerous safety concerns .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"Moreover , reports showed","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"that these kids were n't fleeing violence ,","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"but coming to the U.S. over the perceived notion","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"that we were granting amnesty .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":195,"left":140,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":126,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":114,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":112,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":104,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":99,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":102,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":100,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":111,"left":110,"right":14,"relation":"attri